tm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使这样我也怕死</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re de mo shi nu no wa ko wa i n da</span></p><p begin="2:25.269" end="2:27.128" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:25.269" end="2:25.437">芝</span><span begin="2:25.437" end="2:25.652">居</span> <span begin="2:25.652" end="2:25.936">散</span><span begin="2:25.936" end="2:26.187">々</span><span begin="2:26.187" end="2:26.447">演</span><span begin="2:26.447" end="2:26.592">じ</span><span begin="2:26.592" end="2:26.708">ま</span><span begin="2:26.708" end="2:26.851">し</span><span begin="2:26.851" end="2:27.128">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">戏剧 我已经演够了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">shi ba i sa n za n&apos;e n ji ma shi ta</span></p><p begin="2:27.375" end="2:29.214" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:27.375" end="2:27.530">希</span><span begin="2:27.530" end="2:27.743">望</span> <span begin="2:27.743" end="2:28.032">散</span><span begin="2:28.032" end="2:28.303">々</span><span begin="2:28.303" end="2:28.574">叶</span><span begin="2:28.574" end="2:28.687">え</span><span begin="2:28.687" end="2:28.784">ま</span><span begin="2:28.784" end="2:28.953">し</span><span begin="2:28.953" end="2:29.214">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">希望 已经实现得差不多了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki bo u sa n za n ka na e ma shi ta</span></p><p begin="2:29.463" end="2:31.221" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.463" end="2:29.602">期</span><span begin="2:29.602" end="2:29.828">待</span> <span begin="2:29.828" end="2:30.107">散</span><span begin="2:30.107" end="2:30.353">々</span><span begin="2:30.353" end="2:30.635">応</span><span begin="2:30.635" end="2:30.757">え</span><span begin="2:30.757" end="2:30.868">ま</span><span begin="2:30.868" end="2:31.032">し</span><span begin="2:31.032" end="2:31.221">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">期待 我也回应得差不多了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki ta i sa n za n ko ta e ma shi ta</span></p><p begin=